{"title":"大人先生们的心事","authors":["邵燕祥"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大人先生们的心事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵燕祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哼！党天下，党天下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农居然坐天下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分我土地，抢我工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥着刀把，掌着印把！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好的‘中华民国’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了你们的天下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只有徐图大计呀徐图大计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这怎不叫我咬碎钢牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬碎钢牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“甚么社会主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糟！糟！糟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚么人民民主专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不好！不好！不好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚么共产党领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要！不要！不要！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚么从团结到团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要搅他个乱七八糟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱七八糟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同道们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，来，来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要错过好机会！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁着他们除三害，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搅混河水摸鱼来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的大害是共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫他们下台，叫他们下台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党下台，我们上台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！来！来！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}